Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Job interviews are so nerve-wracking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A Santa-model Shinki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that wanted the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsugaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,do you like Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, you're hired! {I wish I could get a job. ;_;}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hop in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what are the job requirements?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now mush!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.85,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It shines
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:14.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My singing voice is endless
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:21.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My eternal pledge is only for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:28.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wonder if you're your usual self
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:33.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I'll sparkle with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Install dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:46.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}The arms of the clock advance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:53.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and with them so does time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:02:00.18,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}When you are sad, I open my tiny arms
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:06.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and embrace you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:10.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:15.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My singing voice is tender
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:21.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I can remember your shape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:24.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and that wasn't brought about by a program
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:28.24,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Let us experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:33.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}the turmoil in my heart together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:36.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Install dream
