Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Never had a job before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't look like a Career Shinki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't see the standard models working too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your master poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that'll explain the job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay attention, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Your life partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the Multi Movable System!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}As thanks for your continued patronage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}we're holding a Christmas campaign!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}On Christmas Eve, a tiny Santa will visit your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiny Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why'd you apply, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:45.20,Default,,0,0,5,,That scarf would look wonderful on Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.37,Default,,0,0,5,,Isn't it kinda gaudy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:51.47,Default,,0,0,5,,But he would look {\i1}so{\i0} cool in that down jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.77,Default,,0,0,5,,Its price tag has many zeroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,5,,Those gloves are in Master's favorite color.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They look so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they'd be pretty nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Recruiting Christmas Cake decorations..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this looks fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, "Experienced Shinkis only"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's out too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, found anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. They're all asking for Career Shinkis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm the last one out, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The job market's tough. {Don't I know it. ;_;}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't a lot of openings for regular Shinkis to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's amazing that you all got jobs so quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of jobs did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say I work in finances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I work in showbiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Finances and showbiz...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Strarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It is secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you can tell us, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not call me by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann, how about this?
