Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeking a helper for Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas Eve only?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A helper for Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,5,,So you're all working to get a present for your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,5,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,5,,I think it's really sweet of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.00,Default,,0,0,5,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.93,Default,,0,0,5,,We have a lot of houses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,5,,There are a {\i1}lot{\i0} this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.22,Default,,0,0,5,,I can't handle these all alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.81,Default,,0,0,5,,so I've been in a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to visit all of these tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I take pride in my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this job's about delivering dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're delivering dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That was too soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Santa Claus who delivers Christmas dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Santa Claus who delivers Christmas dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My only reward is the smiles of children!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My only reward is the smiles of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's just my image.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you'll get your wage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, tomorrow's gonna be a busy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So get a good night's sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:28.41,Default,,0,0,5,,I am Santa Claus, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,5,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,5,,Whoa, it's a snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,5,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,5,,Thanks, Mr. Snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,5,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, it's rude to peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is your job...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's financial, in a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So how'd your interview go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll only be for tomorrow, but I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That song...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,came from my time in Paris,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when I heard a waiter humming in a podunk cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I had just parted with my lover, and it felt like he was singing for my broken heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the beautiful music.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do a request for my next song!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}this{\i0} is Lene's job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying a street musician works in showbiz is way too much of a stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You were handing out tissues in front of a bank after saying you'd work in finances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not an overstatement?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, when were you ever in Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,An artist can travel around the world within her own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when were you an artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, at least Ann found a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plan's going well for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she's{\i0} still not telling us what kinda job she found...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is for your own safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you would all bear the same cross as I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is her job even legal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be something so dangerous she can't tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A dangerous job...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come home safe, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us to have Christmas together next year, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's a secret, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am well aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So Master, got any plans for tomorrow night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's all have a Christmas party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, tomorrow's Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about I buy a cake on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:52.13,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnCentury\fs27\b1\pos(160,175)\blur1\shad1\4a&B4&\c&H3E26DA&}Shinki Care \NWarning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worth noting that we can't eat cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a killjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd warn everyone just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to tomorrow night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uniform's provided!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever danger comes our way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,delivering presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is Santa Claus's duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We came with a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thanks, Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll divvy up the work from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We've spent more time than I thought we would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's started snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mami, Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the real Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the Santa Claus who delivers Christmas dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only reward is the smiles of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I am Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugaru, I'm finished on my end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugaru, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My left leg's actuator took a hit, it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could have—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to play with a Doberman in the Saito district...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just a little puppy last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I got careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to see a Shinki Shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we need to deliver these presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with that leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I deliver Christmas dre—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,With wounds as deep as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your energy won't last forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the rest of the presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, get yourself to a Shinki Shop as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back as soon as I'm fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you until then, Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! I'll make you proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, there's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you like a delicious cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, balloons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are plenty enough to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Strarf...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whomever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am but a reindeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you would all bear the same cross as I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could this be Strarf's job?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's this bag with a very important present...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall tell you a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In truth, I am no reindeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a term of my employment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,An agreement of confidentiality that I should reveal my true form to nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're troubled over how you can retrieve your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The blizzard's really strong up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so my flight unit will just get blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A Santa Claus balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we use it as a snow break, we may make it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll just have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The starboard side is reeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mend its balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not get blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your thrusters to hold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't leave you two alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines! But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I zoomed in on a balloon that stuck out like a sore thumb,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I saw you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What of your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Financial workers get off early!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay frosty! {She set herself up for this one}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's really strong up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, set thrusters to maximum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, a little to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And Lene, stop singing and help us! {ahaha oh god}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An artist like me can help only through song!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! My tank is near empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I was a bit of a pain to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Tsugaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, everyone, Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mush!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, case closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go buy Master that present!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, sobthin' like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Master will love this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann, you've been sneezing a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'mb feelin' kinda colb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My head's goin' numb...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be an induced fever mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent great time within that blizzard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did our circuitry freeze over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was pretty surprised to find you all collapsed from fever when I got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought a Peach Jellycan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:13.01,Default,,0,0,5,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:15.59,Default,,0,0,5,,Still not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,5,,Well, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,5,,It's my Christmas present for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,5,,I heard this winter would be a cold one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:26.05,Default,,0,0,5,,but these sure came in handy pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:30.31,Default,,0,0,5,,Thank you very much, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:33.25,Default,,0,0,5,,I'm so thirsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:36.06,Default,,0,0,5,,I've got a splitting headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... trifling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've gotta change everyone's ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You need rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann, thanks for these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:21:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! {Holy shit how many times does she say hai in this script.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:26.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I stand here reflected in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:31.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and make something of a foolish face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:39.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Being more gentle than the wind and invincible like the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:44.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,0:22:51.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Here in the forest I am lost in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:57.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to try finding a four-leaf clover
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:04.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}The sun is guiding me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:10.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}towards the miracles of two stars together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:13.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Even if we are hurt on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and ten years pass
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:24.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}this future where I can be with you is what I choose
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:25.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}We will walk on ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:30.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and not miss the sun's sign
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't Hina been a bit odd lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think something's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.82,0:23:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the review period ran out,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and she has to be returned to the manufacturer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:23:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:56.79,Default,,0,0,5,,Next time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:24:00.11,Default,,0,0,5,,"Tonight's the Night! Who's the Strongest Shinki!?"
